          "reviewBody": "This (truth) review can be hidden by school.But if you access this review Please read this and then take decision.\n\nThis is the worst school I have ever seen.All staff, Teachers,Vice Principal,and Principal, Director (chhabra madam) all are Ghatiya(घटिया)..They don't know how to talk to anyone..They all are manipulate with their words during addmission.Once admission has done.They behave so rudely.The facilities they tell during admission children never gets.Even mandatory  computer class, labs and sports class they don't provide.\n\nIf you want a good future for you child don't admit his in this School.",
